&ldquo;Time is the tiny bits of space between one busy moment and the next.&rdquo;
 A friend wrote this and got me thinking, I don&rsquo;t know about you but I am always SO busy these days. I used to think that I was just having a busy week or a busy month. Nup&hellip;that&rsquo;s life :)
It makes you wonder when you&rsquo;ll have time to &lsquo;enjoy&rsquo; life, so much time is spent at work or doing chores or stuck in traffic etc.

So last night we went to see Richard Marx at the Capitol. Yeah&hellip;I know what you&rsquo;re thinking but that&rsquo;s ok, I&rsquo;m not afraid to say that I&rsquo;m a fan and have been for a long time!
Yes it&rsquo;s true I like his voice and his songs, but what I really like is his production and studio band. He always uses the cream of the session muso pool including;
